                            <comment id="12933148" author="hiranya" created="Wed, 17 Nov 2010 20:38:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have introduced a new attribute called &quot;dynamic&quot; to the failover endpoint which is set to true by default. With this the failover endpoint will switch back to the primary endpoint as soon as it becomes available after an error. One can set dynamic=false to get the old static behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
